name: Release 1.44
body:
Feature: Added Azerbaijani as language.

Bugfix: Backup and restore is now also possible with Android 10.

name: Release 1.43
body:
Feature: Update to AndroidX.

Bugfix: Fixed calculation of predicted ovulation.

name: Release 1.42
body: Bugfix: Starting a period after the first day of a predicted cycle is now possible again.

name: Release 1.41
body: Bugfix: Corrected intensity in detail view.

name: Release 1.40
body:
Bugfix: Symbols for details will now be displayed in empty days as well.

Bugfix: Adding and removing days to/from a period now always works correct.

name: Release 1.32
body: Added new symptom, updated help text.

name: Release 1.31
body: Added Hebrew translation.

name: Release 1.30
body:
Events and symptons are now separate lists in the details.

The calendar view will now indicate if there is an event, symptom or note.

Added Greek translation.

name: Release 1.23
body: Details can now also be added or opened in empty days.

name: Release 1.22
body: Added loading screen.

name: Release 1.20
body: Added Polish translation.

name: Release 1.18
body: Updated translations based on Crowdin export and reverted language codes back to their generic form to avoid missing languages when a user selects a regional language setting.

name: Release 1.16
body: Fixed a crash when changing the month using the buttons.

name: Release 1.15
body: Fixed another problem with preferences: a modified setting for luteal phase did not get stored properly.

name: Release 1.13
body: New symptom: headache/migraine

name: Release 1.14
body: Fixed a problem with preferences: changed preferences did not get stored when the app was closed with the preferences opened.

name: Release 1.11
body: Fixed wrong path for assets for "About" and "Help" in Portuguese (Brazil)

name: Release 1.10
body:
Redesign with navigation drawer.

Simple list view with cycle lengths added again.

name: Release 1.06
body: Added translation for Portuguese (Brazil)

name: Release 1.05
body: Updated symptom descriptions.

name: Release 1.04
body: Fixed a bug with preference handling.

name: Release 1.03
body: Added an utility class to deal with shared preferences and avoiding ClassCastException.

name: Release 1.02
body: Correct calculation of day of cycle.

name: Release 1.01
body: Fixed some problems with upgrading from older versions.

name: Release 1.0
body:
* Individual period length.
* Period intensity for every day.
* Notes and symptoms for every day.
* Calendar display with intensity and day of cycle.
* List view with intensity, notes and symptoms.

name: Release 0.35
body: Added maximum cycle length (fixed).

name: Release 0.34
body: Added maximum cycle length.

name: Release 0.33
body: Updated French translation.

name: Release 0.32
body: Added Japanese translation.
